OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfcom investigates campaign
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon Ken Bruce radio show    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ken Bruce's Greatest Hits Radio show is
OL,6, being investigated by Ofcom over the   
OL,7, station's campaign calling for         
OL,8, offenders to be prevented from refusing
OL,9, to attend sentencing hearings.         
OL,11,FThe broadcasting watchdog said on      
OL,12,FMonday it would at look at whether the 
OL,13,Fstation had complied with rules around 
OL,14,Fimpartiality and accuracy.             
OL,16,FThis year's Face the Family petition   
OL,17,Fhas been made directly to Parliament.  
OL,19,FIt was mentioned by a newsreader on    
OL,20,FBruce's show on the station on 13April.
